  "detailed_description": "<h1>Our games you might like</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/716870/extras/852bea13110b5d291b73a5c955658696.webp?t=1757873393\" width=600 height=26 /></span><br><br>Test your reflexes!<br><strong> Gravity Ball </strong> is a game where you aim to make the best score. To do this, avoid obstacles on the path of your ball.<br>You will only need your mouse, just click once so that your ball moves from one wall to another. Each click gives you 1 point.<br>It is an arcade-style game that allows you to relax while watching a video or to entertain yourself while loading another game for example.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/716870/extras/260bba56dfeb98191920f03fd2422c2b.webp?t=1757873393\" width=600 height=26 /></span>",
